                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 European War 1939/16251: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Winant</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-11-01T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 1, 1941—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4906. Please report to the Department by telegraph upon the significance of the
                    visit to London of the Prime Minister of Burma<note n="14" xml:id="d133fn14">U
                        Saw.</note> and any development arising therefrom.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
